- `Schematic.fs:35` `SchematicColor` — reused as the colour value shape for the top‑down surface (C.5.2, C.8).
- `ConstructionView.fs:40` `positiveCta`/`negativeCta` — duplicated CTA colours today; MUST be expressed as the destructive‑gate flavour in `Controls.fs` (J.0, J.2).
