## Risks

Medium: extending `Project.fs` + schema with the table while preserving the
placement anchors slice 001 added (round‑trip + schema‑validation must stay
green for both). The active‑element‑indicator ≥2 px / ≥3:1‑contrast threshold
(AC‑C5) must be asserted from pure geometry/colour values without an Avalonia
render. Keep `Schematic.fs` untouched.

## Hand-off

Record the `OpticalTable` shape, the `Drawer.fs` pure geometry signature
(placement, three rotations, kind, value id → draw geometry), the
`ConstructorTable.fs` layout + named drawing‑weight constants, and the
`Controls.fs` flavour functions, so slice 005 (the FuncUI `Canvas` page +
interaction) can host them and slice 006 (ribbon) can wire the *Trace / View*
show‑CR toggle and the table‑resize control. Carry the `gates:` baseline
YAML block forward.
